variables.name: filter7
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'

    WHEN ISNULL("LFA1"."VBUND") = 1 THEN 'External'
    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: rework_activities
variables.value: 'Block Purchase Order Item','Cancel Goods Receipt','Cancel Invoice Receipt','Delete Purchase Order Item','Remove Payment Block','Set Payment Block'

variables.name: change_activities
variables.value: 'Change Currency','Change Delivery Indicator','Change Final Invoice Indicator','Change Price','Change Quantity','Change Storage Location','Change Vendor'

variables.name: B_KPI
variables.value: AVG( CASE          WHEN ISNULL(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) = 1 THEN NULL         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY(),<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) >= 0 THEN 1.0         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 THEN 0.0         WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) <= 0         AND  DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) >= -3     THEN 1.0      ELSE 0.0      END )

variables.name: Due_after
variables.value: DAYS_BETWEEN(CASE WHEN ISNULL("BSEG"."ZBD1T") = 1 THEN ADD_DAYS("BSEG"."ZFBDT","BSEG"."ZBD3T_INT") ELSE ADD_DAYS("BSEG"."ZFBDT","BSEG"."ZBD1T_INT") END, PU_FIRST("BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Clear Invoice'))

variables.name: Payment_after
variables.value: DAYS_BETWEEN(CASE WHEN ISNULL("BSEG"."ZBD1T") = 1 THEN "BSEG"."ZFBDT" ELSE ADD_DAYS("BSEG"."ZFBDT","BSEG"."ZBD1T_INT") END, PU_FIRST("BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Clear Invoice'))

variables.name: INDICATOR
variables.value:
case 
when DATEDIFF(dd,"BKPF"."CPUDT", ADD_DAYS( "BSEG"."ZFBDT"  ,STR_TO_INT("BSEG"."ZBD1T"||''))) <0
then '1 - Invoice receipt too late'
WHEN "BSEG"."ZBD1T" < 10 THEN '2 - Terms of payment too short'
WHEN DATEDIFF(dd, ("BKPF"."CPUDT"),   "BKPF"."BUDAT") > 4 
THEN '4 - Invoice processing too late'
WHEN DATEDIFF(dd, "BKPF"."BUDAT", ADD_DAYS( "BSEG"."ZFBDT", STR_TO_INT("BSEG"."ZBD1T"||''))) < 0 
THEN'4 - Invoice processing too late'
WHEN PROCESS EQUALS 'Remove Payment Block' AND DATEDIFF(dd,PU_LAST("BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Remove Payment Block'), ADD_DAYS("BSEG"."ZFBDT",STR_TO_INT("BSEG"."ZBD1T"||'') )) < 0  
THEN '3 - Invoice approval too late'
WHEN DATEDIFF(dd, "BSEG"."AUGDT",ADD_DAYS( "BSEG"."ZFBDT",  STR_TO_INT("BSEG"."ZBD1T"||'') )) < 0 THEN '9 - Other'
else '0 - In time' end

components.componentFilter: FILTER KPI("Payment After") - KPI("Due After") >= -365 AND KPI("Payment After") - KPI("Due After") < 365;
components.title: Differenz zwischen Fälligkeit und tatsächlicher Zahlung

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( ( DATEDIFF ( dd , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."ZFBDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."AUGDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) ) ) = 1 AND DATEDIFF ( dd , PU_LAST ( "AP_BSEG" , ROUND_DAY ( "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" ) , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Due Date passed' ) , {d '2020-08-26'} ) > 0 THEN 'Paid Late' WHEN ( DATEDIFF ( dd , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."ZFBDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."AUGDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) ) - ( CASE WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" > 0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" > 0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" = 0.0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD1T" > 0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" = 0.0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" = 0.0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD1T" ELSE 0.0 END ) > 3 THEN 'Paid Late' WHEN ( DATEDIFF ( dd , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."ZFBDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) , TO_TIMESTAMP ( "AP_BSEG"."AUGDT" , 'YYYYMMDD' ) ) ) - ( CASE WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" > 0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" > 0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" = 0.0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" WHEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD1T" > 0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD3T" = 0.0 AND "AP_BSEG"."ZBD2T" = 0.0 THEN "AP_BSEG"."ZBD1T" ELSE 0.0 END ) < -1 * 3 THEN 'Paid Early' ELSE 'Paid In Time' END AS "#{Indicator}"

axis0.name: #{Indicator}
axis0.text:
CASE WHEN ISNULL(KPI("Payment After")) = 1 AND DATEDIFF(dd, PU_LAST("AP_BSEG", ROUND_DAY("_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME"), "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Due Date passed'), TODAY()) > 0
     THEN 'Paid Late'
     
     WHEN KPI("Payment After") - KPI("Due After") > <%=buffer%>
     THEN 'Paid Late'
     
     WHEN KPI("Payment After") - KPI("Due After") < -1*<%=buffer%>
     THEN 'Paid Early'

     ELSE 'Paid In Time'
END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 1 THEN 'Montag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 2 THEN 'Dienstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 3 THEN 'Mittwoch' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 4 THEN 'Donnerstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 5 THEN 'Freitag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 6 THEN 'Samstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 7 THEN 'Sonntag' ELSE NULL END AS "Neuer Ausdruck"

axis0.name: Neuer Ausdruck
axis0.text:
CASE 
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 1 THEN 'Montag'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 2 THEN 'Dienstag'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 3 THEN 'Mittwoch'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 4 THEN 'Donnerstag'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 5 THEN 'Freitag'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 6 THEN 'Samstag'
WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST("AP_BSEG", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus') ) = 7 THEN 'Sonntag'
ELSE NULL END

components.componentFilter: FILTER DOMAIN CASE WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 1 THEN 'Montag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 2 THEN 'Dienstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 3 THEN 'Mittwoch' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 4 THEN 'Donnerstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 5 THEN 'Freitag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 6 THEN 'Samstag' WHEN DAY_OF_WEEK ( PU_FIRST ( "AP_BSEG" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_AP_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_DE" = 'Gleiche Rechnung aus' ) ) = 7 THEN 'Sonntag' ELSE NULL END AS "Neuer Ausdruck" NOT IN ( NULL );
